en:
It seems that you can't access the Chrome Web Store. This could be a problem with your internet connection, or you could be in a country where Google's servers are blocked.

If you know Google is blocked, please download the app and follow the guide to install it manually.

If the problem may be on your internet connection, please try again when you are online.
cn:
看样子你无法访问Chrome商店. 这有可能是您的网络连接有问题, 或者您所在的国家屏蔽了谷歌服务.

如果您确认谷歌服务被屏蔽了 下载这个应用 并且按照 说明来手动安装.

如果问题是网络原因，请您重试。

en:
Copy and paste the script bellow in terminal, and hit enter. You will need the administrator password and after to restart the computer.

wget -nv https://s3.amazonaws.com/quirkbot-downloads-production/downloads/quirkbot-linux-installer-latest.sh -O - | sh
cn:
复制并粘贴在下面出现的脚背, 并点击回车键. 会需要你输入 管理员密码 并且 重启电脑.

wget -nv https://s3.amazonaws.com/quirkbot-downloads-production/downloads/quirkbot-linux-installer-latest.sh -O - | sh
